            <title>[SOLR-185] RequestHandlerUtils - helpers for commit, optimize, and format warnings</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-185</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a helper class to let RequestHandlers share some common code.  This patch adds support for&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; 1. standard &apos;Experimental&apos; format warning  &lt;br/&gt;
 2. getCharsetFromContentType()&lt;br/&gt;
 3. handler parameters ?commit,optimize,waitFlush,waitSearcher&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;this change makes the CommitRequestHandler unnecessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
